{"tid":1748714,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[數據分析] 原來泛民本土可以輕鬆控制17區！但因為一個原因做唔到......","createTime":"2019-11-23T20:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T09:35:05.000Z","uid":470,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23cc82bd4cdfeb5c0ea75275075f9dd043f9f05f","tid":1748714,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"根據2016年立法會選舉各區票站統計<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">18區嘅民選議席，泛民本土都贏多過建制！</span></strong><br />\n連北區西貢都贏！其實離島都贏(6 vs 4)，但計埋當然議員就控制唔到全區<br />\n控制哂17區，保皇狗少條大水喉！<br />\n<br />\n咁點解立法會選舉同區議會選舉爭咁遠？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係因為你同你啲friend無出去投票呀！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. 數據取自2016年立法會選舉結果，所以係以2016年嘅劃界計算<br />\n2. 部分票站跨區幫小票站點票，例如「大嶼山」係一個好撚大嘅選區，「大澳」屬於「大嶼山」但選票會運去東涌集中點算<br />\n3. 泛民建制歸類從嚴處理，部分歸類如下：<br />\n香港島：王維基 泛民 沈志超 建制<br />\n九龍西：李泳漢 狄志遠 建制 何志光 林依麗 唔計<br />\n九龍東：呂永基 泛民 譚香文 唔計<br />\n新界西：馮檢基 呂智恆 泛民 張慧晶 湯詠芝 唔計<br />\n新界東：鄭家富 泛民 方國珊 麥嘉晉 建制</span>"},{"pid":"ba5b664831ddc5312ec27e5969edfa6b36432811","tid":1748714,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa88fc752fa74175b1a1a5de355e5a4a9903fd1","tid":1748714,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票踢走保皇黨 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"bc2878cb870f24875e2159ae453b103c4f6fc7a2","tid":1748714,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4324138b881e6430d5c480925739b043db72ff39","tid":1748714,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:13:28.000